'''皮翼龍'''（學名：''Dermodactylus''）意為「有皮的手指」，是[[翼龍目|翼龍目]][[翼手龍亞目|翼手龍亞目]]的一屬，化石發現於[[美國|美國]][[懷俄明州|懷俄明州]]的[[莫里遜組|莫里遜組]]，年代為[[侏羅紀|侏羅紀]]晚期（[[啟莫里階|啟莫里階]]到[[提通階|提通階]]）。

==歷史與分類==
皮翼龍的[[正模標本|正模標本]]（編號YPM 2000）是一個右手的第四[[掌骨|掌骨]]，只有末端部分，是由[[塞繆爾·溫德爾·威利斯頓|塞繆爾·溫德爾·威利斯頓]]（Samuel Wendell Williston）發現於懷俄明州[[科莫崖|科莫崖]]。皮翼龍是[[北美洲|北美洲]]第一個發現、命名的翼龍類<ref name=PW96a>{{cite book |last=Wellnhofer |first=Peter |title=The Illustrated Encyclopedia of Pterosaurs |url=https://archive.org/details/illustratedencyc0000well_v0o5 |origyear=1991 |year=1996 |publisher=Barnes and Noble Books |location=New York |isbn=0-7607-0154-7 |pages= p. 105 }}</ref>。[[奧塞內爾·查利斯·馬什|奧塞內爾·查利斯·馬什]]（Othniel Charles Marsh）最初將牠們歸類於[[翼手龍屬|翼手龍屬]]的一個種（''P. montanus''）<ref name=OCM78>{{cite journal |last=Marsh |first=Othniel Charles |year=1878 |title=New pterodactyl from the Jurassic of the Rocky Mountains |journal=American Journal of Science, series 3 |volume=16 |pages=233–234 }}</ref>，後來將牠們建立為獨立的屬；種名在[[拉丁文|拉丁文]]意為「來自山脈的」。馬什曾將一些手部骨頭、牙齒、[[脊椎|脊椎]]、[[肩胛骨|肩胛骨]]、[[鳥喙骨|鳥喙骨]]歸類於皮翼龍<ref name=OCM81>{{cite journal |last=Marsh |first=Othniel Charles |year=1881 |title=Note on American pterodactyls |journal=American Journal of Science, series 3 |volume=21 |pages=342–343 }}</ref>，但這些化石過大，與皮翼龍的原始化石不符合<ref name=PW78>{{cite book |last=Wellnhofer |first=Peter |title=Pterosauria |series=''Handbuch der Paläoherpetologie, Teil'' '''19''' |year=1978 |publisher=Gustav Fischer |location=Stuttgart |isbn=3437302698 |pages=p. 65 }}</ref>。

皮翼龍屬於翼手龍亞目，但由於只有一塊手部骨頭，詳細的分類關係仍不確定<ref name=PW96b>{{cite book |last=Wellnhofer |first=Peter |title=The Illustrated Encyclopedia of Pterosaurs |url=https://archive.org/details/illustratedencyc0000well_v0o5 |origyear=1991 |year=1996 |publisher=Barnes and Noble Books |location=New York |isbn=0-7607-0154-7 |pages= p. 107 }}</ref>。在2003年，[[肯尼思·卡彭特|肯尼思·卡彭特]]（Kenneth Carpenter）根據該骨頭的形狀，認為皮翼龍不屬於[[鳥掌翼龍科|鳥掌翼龍科]]；鳥掌翼龍科通常具有頭冠、大型牙齒、短尾巴<ref name=KCetal03>{{cite book |last=Carpenter |first=Kenneth |coauthors=Unwin, David M.; Cloward, Karen; Miles, Clifford A.; and Miles, Clark |chapter=A new scaphognathine pterosaur from the Upper Jurassic Formation of Wyoming, USA |editor=Buffetaut, Eric; and Mazin, Jean- Michel (eds.) |title=Evolution and Palaeobiology of Pterosaurs |year=2003 |series=''Geological Society of London, Special Publications'', '''217''' |publisher=Geological Society of London |location=London |pages=45-54 |url=https://scientists.dmns.org/sites/kencarpenter/PDFs%20of%20publications/Harpactognathus.pdf |isbn=1-86239-143-2 |accessdate=2007-03-02 }}{{dead link|date=2018年1月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。由於化石稀少，皮翼龍目前是個[[疑名|疑名]]<ref name=KCetal03/><ref name=JC96>{{cite journal |last=Harris |first=Jerald D. |coauthors=Carpenter, Kenneth |year=1996 |title=A large pterodactyloid from the Morrison Formation (Late Jurassic) of Garden Park, Colorado |journal=Neues Jahrbuch für Geologie und Paläontologie Monatshefte |volume=8 |pages=473–484 |url=https://scientists.dmns.org/sites/kencarpenter/PDFs%20of%20publications/Kepodactylus.pdf |accessdate=2007-03-02 |archive-date=2007-09-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070927214839/https://scientists.dmns.org/sites/kencarpenter/PDFs%20of%20publications/Kepodactylus.pdf |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref name=DFG06>{{cite book |last=Glut |first=Donald F. |title=Dinosaurs: The Encyclopedia. 4th Supplement |year=2006 |publisher=McFarland & Company, Inc. |location=Jefferson, North Carolina |isbn=0-7864-2295-5 |pages=p. 598 |chapter=Dermodactylus }}</ref><ref name=KFS06>{{cite book |last=King |first=Lorin R. |coauthors=Foster, John R.; and Scheetz, Rodney D. |chapter=New pterosaur specimens from the Morrison Formation and a summary of the Late Jurassic pterosaur record of the Rocky Mountain region|editor=Foster, John R.; and Lucas, Spencer G. (eds.) |title=Paleontology and Geology of the Upper Morrison Formation |year=2006 |series=New Mexico Museum of Natural History and Science Bulletin, '''36''' |publisher=New Mexico Museum of Natural History and Science |location=Albuquerque, New Mexico |pages=149-161 }}</ref>。在[[大衛·安文|大衛·安文]]（David M. Unwin）的近期翼龍類研究中，並沒有提到皮翼龍<ref name=DMU06>{{cite book |last=Unwin |first=David M. |title=The Pterosaurs: From Deep Time |url=https://archive.org/details/pterosaursfromde00unwi |year=2006 |publisher=Pi Press |location=New York |isbn= 0-13-146308-X |pages=[https://archive.org/details/pterosaursfromde00unwi/page/1 1]-347 }}</ref>。

==古生物學==
馬什認為皮翼龍的翼展為1.5到1.8公尺，但這是包含其他的化石在內<ref name=OCM81/>。[[彼得·沃爾赫費爾|彼得·沃爾赫費爾]]（Peter Wellnhofer）根據唯一的化石，估計皮翼龍的翼展為1公尺<ref name=PW96a/>。John Foster估計皮翼龍的體重為3.3公斤。皮翼龍可能是種小型的[[肉食性|肉食性]]飛行動物<ref name=JF03>{{cite book |last=Foster |first=John R. |title=Paleoecological Analysis of the Vertebrate Fauna of the Morrison Formation (Upper Jurassic), Rocky Mountain Region, U.S.A. |year=2003 |series=New Mexico Museum of Natural History and Science Bulletin, '''23''' |publisher=New Mexico Museum of Natural History and Science |location=Albuquerque, New Mexico |pages=p. 37}}</ref>。

